text: Metamulciber ziczac is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1947. It is known from Papua New Guinea.BioLib.cz - Metamulciber ziczac. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1947
title: Metamulciber ziczac
